description: As Seen on TV, the Lynx Cleaning System eliminates the need for multiple cleaning tools and creates a perfectly organized storage space. This docking station neatly stores all of the included cleaning tools in one place. The three-in-one mop, duster, and broom are all at your fingertips, and changing the attachments is easy. Simply click to connect the attachment and twist to disconnect when you're finished cleaning. The broom attachment has dense, soft bristles that are perfect for indoor and outdoor use, the mop attachment is ultra-absorbent with a scrubbing layer, and the duster can be used with either wet or dry pads for quick cleaning.
